{"tid":1424774,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔有冇可能整個「正負評詳情」","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:48:11.000Z","uid":144187,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d7728ed55be8a51bb4297c1fd945d5213eca51f","tid":1424774,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n<br />\n睇完澄清後，突然諗到，可唔可以喺 1樓個正負評隔離，整個詳情制，等大家一下就睇到詳細數據?<br />\n<br />\n好似咁 : <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSihUTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSihUTa.jpg&h=c3025d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一㩒就會提供類似上圖嘅資料（例如 P牌比例及數字 / 正負評速率）去防三毛帶風向？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uepQvpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuepQvpL.jpg&h=c0126205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得諗得過請幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841bae8bba71c28d77bd79bfddd150e50caf6b34","tid":1424774,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6cba3393fdf54fbdebd0c83838017e441701119d","tid":1424774,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"60e4b547bde9fce51bfa739e3840f7828c6de55a","tid":1424774,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"affc11465c91b6b61a37e4c1c85c93f9c43a1a0f","tid":1424774,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:32:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cda1f771f9656351b2cbf0baab1740f1309b5999","tid":1424774,"uid":254188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"4460a4250e63a9359491ba0377b8f57ee623ea89","tid":14247